    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>In this chapter we add an installation script. In the explanations of the component, I described what you use it for.<!-- \\index{module!installation script} --></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>For impatient people: Look at the changed program code in the <a href=\"https://codeberg.org/astrid/j4examplecode/compare/t33...t34\">diff view</a>[^github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t33...t34] and copy these changes into your development version.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"step-by-step\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#step-by-step\" aria-label=\"step by step permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Step by step</h2>\n<p>In this section we will create a script that will be executed on specific events during the installation.</p>\n<h3 id=\"new-fiels\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#new-fiels\" aria-label=\"new fiels permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>New fiels</h3>\n<h4 id=\"module\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#module\" aria-label